					"type": 23,
					"value": "Baelen, the Mushroom Hunter, has fallen into a field of dangerous Bibberbang. He's stuck in a small clearing, away from his bag containing a single teleportation scroll. If he moves, the mushrooms may release spores that will explode if they reach his lit torch nearby.\n\n"
